<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 12 (Xinhua) -- PICC Property, one of the three
subsidiaries of the country's biggest insurer, today signed
agreements with a Chinese bank syndicate and four major Chinese
exporters for a 450 million US dollar-worth policy against the
buyer's export credit for Iran's Terran subway system.
</P>
