managed to get involved in export credit market through creating a
consortium.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese bank syndicate consisting of ten commercial and
policy banks will provide 430 million dollars in export credit
loans of the total of 530 million dollars, and it included the
Bank of China, the Construction Bank of China, the Industrial and
Commercial Bank of China, and the Export and Import Bank of
China. 
