<HEADLINE> 38 Injured In explosion In Eastern Sri Lanka </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, August 12 (Xinhua)-- At least 38 people were seriously
injured in an explosion around midnight Sunday at the Mamangam
Pillayar Kovil premises in Batticaloa Town in Eastern Province of
Sri Lanka, according to police sources here today.
</P>
