<TEXT>
<P>
NANNING, August 12 (Xinhua) -- Pingguo Aluminum Company,
China's largest aluminum base in south China's Guangxi Zhuang
Autonomous Region, has increased its production to 280 tons of
aluminum every day.
</P>
