other officials.
</P>
<P>
Than Shwe will be the first Myanmar leader to visit Malaysia
since the SLORC came to power in 1988.
</P>
<P>
Than Shwe's visit to Malaysia, a member of the Association of
Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN), also came after Myanmar's
admittance as an observer of ASEAN last month at the Jakarta ASEAN
ministerial meeting.
</P>
<P>
Myanmar and Malaysia established diplomatic relations in early
1958. However, the trade volume between the two countries has been
very small since then.
</P>
<P>
